item.title: Project 2: Modeling, Testing, and Predicting
item.description: NAME: Ayanna Fisher EID: adf2353 DUE: 05/07/2021 Introduction This dataset details Google Play Store apps and their corresponding qualities. With 10,841 observations, there are 13 variables, App, Category, Rating, Reviews, Size, Installs, Type, Price, Content Rating, Genres, Last Updated, Current Version, and Android Version. Of the 13 variables, this project will focus on variables Category, Rating, Reviews, Size, and Type. After tidying the dataset and omitting any NA values, there will be a total of 7,088 observations to manipulate in this project.
